{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"502","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/HTTP/Status/502","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>這是一個<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTTP\">HTTP</a> 錯誤代碼，表示“網關錯誤”。</p>\n\n<p>一個伺服器(<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Server\">server</a>)可以在一個客戶端(譬如網頁瀏覽器)和其他上游伺服器之間充當網關或代理(中間人)。當你請求訪問一個鏈接(<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/URL\">URL</a>)，網關伺服器可以從上游伺服器傳達你的請求。\"502\" 意味著上游伺服器返回了一個無效的響應。</p>\n\n<p>正常情況下上游伺服器是不會宕機的(如沒有提供對網關/代理的相應)，簡單來説就是作爲網關/代理不明白相同的數據交換協議。&nbsp;因特網協議(<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">protocols</a>)是非常明確的，所以 502 通常意味著有一臺或者多臺機器沒有正確或者完整的程式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Response_codes\">HTTP 響應代碼列表</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"這是一個HTTP 錯誤代碼，表示“網關錯誤”。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"502","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"502","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"502","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"502","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/http/status/502","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/http/status/502/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"502 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}